snippet.title: Obscure Game Theater - Godzilla - C64 (RE: Playitbogart's!)
snippet.description: Just for the sake of argument, I thought I'd throw yet another not so great Godzilla game out into the water. This one is short and sweet thankfully due to my insomnia. It's got some nice shiny death tolls for ya though. Enjoy!
